// —— 21. Vintage as Recession-Proof Investment ——
const recessionEn = p("vintage-recession-investment", "en", "vintage-jewelry-recession-proof-investment", "Vintage Jewelry as Recession-Proof Investment", "Why tangible luxury like vintage jewelry can hold value during economic uncertainty. Rarity, demand, and diversification.", [{ type: "h2", text: "Tangible Assets in Uncertain Times" }, { type: "p", text: "During economic downturns, investors often seek assets that are tangible and historically resilient. Gold has long played that role; fine jewelry—especially vintage and estate pieces in precious metals and genuine stones—shares some of that character. It is wearable, portable, and not tied to a single currency or market." }, { type: "p", text: "Vintage jewelry is also scarce. It cannot be reproduced exactly; supply is limited by what was made in the past. Demand from collectors, brides, and fashion-conscious buyers has remained strong, supporting prices for quality pieces." }, { type: "h2", text: "Diversification and Long-Term View" }, { type: "p", text: "Jewelry should not replace a balanced investment strategy, but it can be part of a diversified approach. Buy pieces you love and would wear; document and insure them. Over the long term, well-chosen vintage and estate jewelry has often held or increased in value." }, { type: "h3", text: "Building a Resilient Collection" }, { type: "p", text: "Focus on quality: fine metals, genuine stones, recognizable periods, and good condition. Buy from trusted sources like SÁV+ so you know what you are getting. Explore our curated vintage and estate collection for pieces that combine beauty with lasting value." }], [1, 3], [{ question: "Is vintage jewelry a good investment in a recession?", answer: "Tangible luxury like vintage jewelry can hold value due to scarcity and demand. It is not a substitute for a full investment strategy but can diversify a portfolio." }, { question: "What makes vintage jewelry hold value?", answer: "Scarcity (limited supply), quality materials, craftsmanship, and sustained demand from collectors and buyers support long-term value." }, { question: "Should I buy vintage jewelry for investment?", answer: "Buy pieces you love and would wear; treat investment potential as a bonus. Document and insure them. Quality and provenance matter for resale." }]);
const recessionEs = p("vintage-recession-investment", "es", "joyas-vintage-inversion-segura", "Joyas Vintage como Inversión Segura", "Por qué el lujo tangible como la joyería vintage puede mantener valor en incertidumbre económica. Rareza, demanda y diversificación.", [{ type: "h2", text: "Activos tangibles en tiempos inciertos" }, { type: "p", text: "En recesiones, los inversores suelen buscar activos tangibles e históricamente resilientes. El oro ha cumplido ese papel; la joyería fina—sobre todo vintage y de herencia en metales preciosos y piedras genuinas—comparte parte de ese carácter. Es llevable, portable y no ligada a una sola moneda o mercado." }, { type: "p", text: "La joyería vintage también es escasa. No puede reproducirse exactamente; la oferta está limitada por lo que se hizo en el pasado. La demanda de coleccionistas, novias y compradores con conciencia de moda se ha mantenido, apoyando los precios de piezas de calidad." }, { type: "h2", text: "Diversificación y visión a largo plazo" }, { type: "p", text: "La joyería no debe sustituir una estrategia de inversión equilibrada, pero puede formar parte de un enfoque diversificado. Compra piezas que te gusten y llevarías; documéntalas y asegúralas. A largo plazo, la joyería vintage y de herencia bien elegida ha mantenido o aumentado valor." }, { type: "h3", text: "Construir una colección resiliente" }, { type: "p", text: "Enfócate en calidad: metales finos, piedras genuinas, épocas reconocibles y buen estado. Compra en fuentes de confianza como SÁV+. Explora nuestra colección curada." }], [1, 3], [{ question: "¿La joyería vintage es buena inversión en recesión?", answer: "El lujo tangible como la joyería vintage puede mantener valor por escasez y demanda. No sustituye una estrategia de inversión completa pero puede diversificar." }, { question: "¿Qué hace que la joyería vintage mantenga valor?", answer: "La escasez, materiales de calidad, artesanía y demanda sostenida de coleccionistas y compradores apoyan el valor a largo plazo." }, { question: "¿Debo comprar joyería vintage como inversión?", answer: "Compra piezas que te gusten y llevarías; trata el potencial de inversión como plus. Documéntalas y asegúralas. La calidad y procedencia importan para la reventa." }]);

// —— 22. Benefits of Pre-Owned Luxury ——
const preOwnedEn = p("benefits-pre-owned-luxury", "en", "benefits-of-pre-owned-luxury", "Benefits of Pre-Owned Luxury: Why Buy Vintage and Estate Jewelry", "Save money, get unique design, and support sustainability. The advantages of buying pre-owned luxury jewelry.", [{ type: "h2", text: "Value and Uniqueness" }, { type: "p", text: "Pre-owned luxury jewelry often costs less than equivalent new pieces while offering the same or better materials—gold, platinum, diamonds, and colored stones. You also get design that is no longer in production: Art Deco, Victorian, mid-century, and one-of-a-kind estate pieces that stand out from mass-produced current collections." }, { type: "p", text: "Estate and vintage jewelry has history. Each piece has a story; wearing it connects you to the past and to craftsmanship that valued durability and beauty. For many, that narrative is part of the appeal." }, { type: "h2", text: "Sustainability and Ethics" }, { type: "p", text: "Buying pre-owned means no new mining or manufacturing for that piece. You reuse what already exists, which reduces environmental impact and supports a circular approach to luxury. It is one of the most direct ways to enjoy fine jewelry while aligning with sustainable values." }, { type: "h3", text: "Where to Shop Pre-Owned" }, { type: "p", text: "Trusted estate dealers and curated collections offer authenticated pieces with clear descriptions. In Florida, Bradenton, Sarasota, and Miami have strong markets; online platforms like SÁV+ bring curated vintage and estate jewelry to you. Explore our collection for pre-owned luxury you can wear with pride." }], [1, 3], [{ question: "Is pre-owned jewelry cheaper than new?", answer: "Often yes. You can get the same or better materials and unique design at lower prices than equivalent new pieces." }, { question: "Is pre-owned luxury jewelry sustainable?", answer: "Yes. Reusing existing pieces avoids new extraction and manufacturing, supporting a circular economy." }, { question: "Where can I buy pre-owned luxury jewelry?", answer: "Estate jewelry dealers, curated online collections, and reputable vintage specialists. Florida has a strong market; trusted online sources like SÁV+ offer curated selections." }]);
const preOwnedEs = p("benefits-pre-owned-luxury", "es", "beneficios-del-lujo-pre-owned", "Beneficios del Lujo Pre-owned: Por Qué Comprar Joyería Vintage y de Herencia", "Ahorra dinero, consigue diseño único y apoya la sostenibilidad. Las ventajas de comprar joyería de lujo de segunda mano.", [{ type: "h2", text: "Valor y singularidad" }, { type: "p", text: "La joyería de lujo de segunda mano suele costar menos que piezas nuevas equivalentes y ofrece los mismos o mejores materiales. También obtienes diseño que ya no se produce: Art Decó, victoriano, mid-century y piezas de herencia únicas que destacan." }, { type: "p", text: "La joyería de herencia y vintage tiene historia. Cada pieza tiene una historia; llevarla te conecta con el pasado y con una artesanía que valoraba durabilidad y belleza." }, { type: "h2", text: "Sostenibilidad y ética" }, { type: "p", text: "Comprar de segunda mano significa que no hay nueva minería ni fabricación para esa pieza. Reutilizas lo que ya existe, lo que reduce el impacto ambiental y apoya un enfoque circular del lujo." }, { type: "h3", text: "Dónde comprar pre-owned" }, { type: "p", text: "Comerciantes de herencia de confianza y colecciones curadas ofrecen piezas autenticadas. En Florida, Bradenton, Sarasota y Miami hay mercados fuertes; plataformas como SÁV+ llevan joyería vintage y de herencia curada hasta ti. Explora nuestra colección." }], [1, 3], [{ question: "¿La joyería pre-owned es más barata que la nueva?", answer: "A menudo sí. Puedes obtener los mismos o mejores materiales y diseño único a precios más bajos que piezas nuevas equivalentes." }, { question: "¿El lujo pre-owned es sostenible?", answer: "Sí. Reutilizar piezas existentes evita nueva extracción y fabricación, apoyando una economía circular." }, { question: "¿Dónde comprar joyería de lujo pre-owned?", answer: "Comerciantes de joyería de herencia, colecciones online curadas y especialistas vintage serios. Florida tiene un mercado fuerte; fuentes online como SÁV+ ofrecen selecciones curadas." }]);

// —— 23. Building a Capsule Jewelry Collection ——
const capsuleEn = p("capsule-jewelry-collection", "en", "building-a-capsule-jewelry-collection", "Building a Capsule Jewelry Collection: Less Is More", "How to build a small, versatile jewelry collection that works for every occasion. Quality over quantity.", [{ type: "h2", text: "What Is a Capsule Jewelry Collection?" }, { type: "p", text: "A capsule jewelry collection is a curated set of pieces that work together and cover most occasions—everyday, work, and special events. Instead of many rarely worn items, you choose a few high-quality pieces: perhaps a pair of studs, a versatile necklace, a bracelet, and one or two statement rings. Each piece earns its place." }, { type: "p", text: "Vintage and estate jewelry fits the capsule idea well. You get unique design, fine materials, and lasting quality. A single vintage Cartier or Art Deco piece can anchor the collection; simpler gold and pearl pieces can be worn daily." }, { type: "h2", text: "How to Build Yours" }, { type: "p", text: "Start with pieces you will wear most: studs or small hoops, a simple chain or pendant, a classic bracelet. Add one or two statement pieces for occasions. Choose metals that mix (e.g., all gold tones) so everything coordinates. Quality and versatility matter more than number of pieces." }, { type: "h3", text: "Finding Capsule-Worthy Pieces" }, { type: "p", text: "Curated vintage and estate collections are ideal for building a capsule—you see edited selections of quality pieces. At SÁV+ we select for design, materials, and wearability. Explore our collection to find the pieces that will form your own capsule collection." }], [1, 3], [{ question: "How many pieces are in a capsule jewelry collection?", answer: "There is no fixed number. Often 5–15 pieces that mix and match for different occasions. The idea is quality and versatility, not quantity." }, { question: "Should my capsule be all one metal?", answer: "Mixing similar tones (e.g., yellow and rose gold) usually works. Some prefer one metal for cohesion; others mix. Choose what you will wear most." }, { question: "Is vintage jewelry good for a capsule collection?", answer: "Yes. Vintage pieces offer unique design and quality at often better value. They can be the foundation or the statement pieces in a capsule." }]);
const capsuleEs = p("capsule-jewelry-collection", "es", "crear-coleccion-capsula-joyas", "Crear una Colección Cápsula de Joyas: Menos Es Más", "Cómo construir una colección pequeña y versátil que funcione para cada ocasión. Calidad sobre cantidad.", [{ type: "h2", text: "¿Qué es una colección cápsula de joyas?" }, { type: "p", text: "Una colección cápsula es un conjunto curado de piezas que funcionan juntas y cubren la mayoría de ocasiones. En lugar de muchas piezas que rara vez llevas, eliges pocas de alta calidad: unos pendientes, un collar versátil, una pulsera y uno o dos anillos de impacto. Cada pieza se gana su lugar." }, { type: "p", text: "La joyería vintage y de herencia encaja bien con la idea cápsula. Obtienes diseño único, materiales finos y calidad duradera." }, { type: "h2", text: "Cómo construir la tuya" }, { type: "p", text: "Empieza con piezas que llevarás más: pendientes, una cadena o colgante, una pulsera clásica. Añade una o dos piezas de impacto para ocasiones. Elige metales que combinen. La calidad y la versatilidad importan más que el número." }, { type: "h3", text: "Encontrar piezas dignas de cápsula" }, { type: "p", text: "Las colecciones vintage y de herencia curadas son ideales para construir una cápsula. En SÁV+ seleccionamos por diseño, materiales y llevabilidad. Explora nuestra colección." }], [1, 3], [{ question: "¿Cuántas piezas tiene una colección cápsula?", answer: "No hay número fijo. A menudo 5–15 piezas que se mezclan para distintas ocasiones. La idea es calidad y versatilidad." }, { question: "¿Mi cápsula debe ser de un solo metal?", answer: "Mezclar tonos similares suele funcionar. Algunos prefieren un metal para cohesión; otros mezclan. Elige lo que más llevarás." }, { question: "¿La joyería vintage es buena para una cápsula?", answer: "Sí. Las piezas vintage ofrecen diseño único y calidad, a menudo con mejor valor. Pueden ser la base o las piezas de impacto." }]);

// —— 24. Best Vintage Finds in Bradenton & Sarasota ——
const bradentonEn = p("vintage-finds-bradenton-sarasota", "en", "best-vintage-finds-bradenton-sarasota", "Best Vintage Finds in Bradenton & Sarasota", "Why Florida’s Gulf Coast is a destination for estate and vintage jewelry. Where to look and what to expect in Bradenton and Sarasota.", [{ type: "h2", text: "Florida’s Estate Jewelry Scene" }, { type: "p", text: "Bradenton and Sarasota are part of a strong Florida estate jewelry market. Retirees, snowbirds, and families have brought heirloom and vintage pieces to the region for decades; estate sales, consignment shops, and dedicated jewelers have built a thriving trade. The result is a concentration of quality vintage and estate pieces available to locals and visitors." }, { type: "p", text: "You can find Art Deco rings, Victorian lockets, mid-century gold, and one-of-a-kind estate pieces. Dealers in the area often have deep inventory and knowledge of period styles and materials." }, { type: "h2", text: "Shopping for Vintage on the Gulf Coast" }, { type: "p", text: "Visit local jewelers, estate dealers, and consignment stores. Ask about provenance and request documentation when possible. Online curated collections also serve the region—SÁV+ offers vintage and estate jewelry to Florida and beyond, so you can shop from home while still benefiting from a Florida-focused selection." }, { type: "h3", text: "What to Look For" }, { type: "p", text: "Look for hallmarks, condition, and seller reputation. Whether in person or online, choose dealers who describe pieces clearly and stand behind authenticity. Explore SÁV+’s curated collection for estate and vintage pieces that reflect the quality and variety of Florida’s market." }], [1, 3], [{ question: "Why is Florida good for estate jewelry?", answer: "Florida has a large population of retirees and families with heirloom pieces, plus a strong network of estate dealers, jewelers, and consignment shops." }, { question: "Where can I find vintage jewelry in Bradenton?", answer: "Local jewelers, estate dealers, consignment stores, and online curated collections that serve the area. Ask for documentation and buy from trusted sources." }, { question: "Is Sarasota good for vintage jewelry shopping?", answer: "Yes. Sarasota is part of Florida’s active estate jewelry market. You can find period pieces and one-of-a-kind estate jewelry from local and online dealers." }]);
const bradentonEs = p("vintage-finds-bradenton-sarasota", "es", "hallazgos-vintage-bradenton-sarasota", "Hallazgos Vintage en Bradenton y Sarasota", "Por qué la costa del Golfo de Florida es un destino para joyería de herencia y vintage. Dónde buscar y qué esperar en Bradenton y Sarasota.", [{ type: "h2", text: "La escena de joyería de herencia en Florida" }, { type: "p", text: "Bradenton y Sarasota forman parte de un mercado fuerte de joyería de herencia en Florida. Jubilados y familias han traído piezas de herencia y vintage a la región durante décadas; ventas de herencia, tiendas de consignación y joyeros dedicados han construido un comercio próspero." }, { type: "p", text: "Puedes encontrar anillos Art Decó, medallones victorianos, oro mid-century y piezas de herencia únicas. Los comerciantes de la zona suelen tener inventario profundo y conocimiento de estilos y materiales de época." }, { type: "h2", text: "Comprar vintage en la costa del Golfo" }, { type: "p", text: "Visita joyeros locales, comerciantes de herencia y tiendas de consignación. Pregunta por la procedencia y pide documentación cuando sea posible. Las colecciones online curadas también sirven a la región—SÁV+ ofrece joyería vintage y de herencia en Florida y más allá." }, { type: "h3", text: "Qué buscar" }, { type: "p", text: "Busca contrastes, estado y reputación del vendedor. Ya sea en persona u online, elige comerciantes que describan las piezas con claridad y respalden la autenticidad. Explora la colección curada de SÁV+." }], [1, 3], [{ question: "¿Por qué Florida es buena para joyería de herencia?", answer: "Florida tiene una gran población de jubilados y familias con piezas de herencia, además de una red fuerte de comerciantes de herencia, joyeros y tiendas de consignación." }, { question: "¿Dónde encontrar joyería vintage en Bradenton?", answer: "Joyeros locales, comerciantes de herencia, tiendas de consignación y colecciones online curadas que sirven el área. Pide documentación y compra en fuentes de confianza." }, { question: "¿Sarasota es buena para comprar joyería vintage?", answer: "Sí. Sarasota forma parte del activo mercado de joyería de herencia de Florida. Puedes encontrar piezas de época y joyería de herencia única." }]);

// —— 25. Why Florida is the Capital of Estate Jewelry ——
const floridaCapitalEn = p("florida-capital-estate-jewelry", "en", "why-florida-is-capital-of-estate-jewelry", "Why Florida Is the Capital of Estate Jewelry", "From Miami to Sarasota, Florida leads in estate and vintage jewelry. Demographics, dealers, and why the state dominates the market.", [{ type: "h2", text: "Demographics and Supply" }, { type: "p", text: "Florida’s population includes a high concentration of retirees and seasonal residents who have accumulated jewelry over a lifetime. When estates are settled, fine jewelry often comes to market—rings, necklaces, bracelets, and brooches from the Victorian era through the late 20th century. This steady supply has attracted dealers, auction houses, and collectors, making Florida one of the nation’s leading markets for estate jewelry." }, { type: "p", text: "Cities like Miami, Sarasota, Bradenton, Naples, and Palm Beach have especially active scenes. You can find everything from Art Deco and Edwardian pieces to mid-century modern and signed designer jewelry." }, { type: "h2", text: "A Hub for Dealers and Buyers" }, { type: "p", text: "Florida’s estate jewelry ecosystem includes brick-and-mortar jewelers, dedicated estate dealers, consignment shops, and online platforms that source from the region. Buyers from across the U.S. and abroad shop Florida inventory in person or online. SÁV+ is part of this ecosystem, curating vintage and estate pieces for customers in Florida and beyond." }, { type: "h3", text: "Shopping Florida Estate Jewelry" }, { type: "p", text: "Whether you are in Florida or shopping from elsewhere, you can access the state’s estate jewelry market through trusted dealers and curated collections. Look for clear descriptions, documentation, and authenticity guarantees. Explore SÁV+’s collection for estate and vintage jewelry that reflects the quality and diversity of Florida’s market." }], [1, 3], [{ question: "Why does Florida have so much estate jewelry?", answer: "A large retiree and seasonal population has brought a lifetime of jewelry to the state. When estates are settled, pieces enter the market, attracting dealers and buyers." }, { question: "Which Florida cities are best for estate jewelry?", answer: "Miami, Sarasota, Bradenton, Naples, and Palm Beach are among the most active. Dealers and inventory are concentrated in these areas." }, { question: "Can I buy Florida estate jewelry online?", answer: "Yes. Many Florida-based dealers and curated platforms like SÁV+ sell online, so you can access the market from anywhere." }]);
const floridaCapitalEs = p("florida-capital-estate-jewelry", "es", "por-que-florida-es-capital-joyas-herencia", "Por qué Florida es la Capital de las Joyas de Herencia", "De Miami a Sarasota, Florida lidera en joyería de herencia y vintage. Demografía, comerciantes y por qué el estado domina el mercado.", [{ type: "h2", text: "Demografía y oferta" }, { type: "p", text: "La población de Florida incluye una alta concentración de jubilados y residentes estacionales que han acumulado joyería durante toda la vida. Cuando se liquidan herencias, la joyería fina suele llegar al mercado. Esta oferta constante ha atraído a comerciantes, casas de subastas y coleccionistas." }, { type: "p", text: "Ciudades como Miami, Sarasota, Bradenton, Naples y Palm Beach tienen escenas especialmente activas." }, { type: "h2", text: "Un centro para comerciantes y compradores" }, { type: "p", text: "El ecosistema de joyería de herencia de Florida incluye joyeros con tienda, comerciantes de herencia, tiendas de consignación y plataformas online que se abastecen en la región. SÁV+ forma parte de este ecosistema, curando piezas vintage y de herencia para clientes en Florida y más allá." }, { type: "h3", text: "Comprar joyería de herencia en Florida" }, { type: "p", text: "Ya estés en Florida o comprando desde fuera, puedes acceder al mercado de joyería de herencia del estado a través de comerciantes de confianza y colecciones curadas. Explora la colección de SÁV+." }], [1, 3], [{ question: "¿Por qué Florida tiene tanta joyería de herencia?", answer: "Una gran población de jubilados y residentes estacionales ha traído una vida de joyería al estado. Cuando se liquidan herencias, las piezas entran al mercado." }, { question: "¿Qué ciudades de Florida son mejores para joyería de herencia?", answer: "Miami, Sarasota, Bradenton, Naples y Palm Beach están entre las más activas." }, { question: "¿Puedo comprar joyería de herencia de Florida online?", answer: "Sí. Muchos comerciantes con base en Florida y plataformas curadas como SÁV+ venden online." }]);

// —— 26. Buying Vintage Online Safely ——
const buyingOnlineEn = p("buying-vintage-online", "en", "buying-vintage-online-safely", "Buying Vintage Online Safely: A Guide to Trust and Authenticity", "How to buy vintage and estate jewelry online with confidence. Red flags, trust signals, and protecting your purchase.", [{ type: "h2", text: "Choosing Trusted Sellers" }, { type: "p", text: "Buy from established dealers or curated platforms that specialize in vintage and estate jewelry. Look for clear photos (multiple angles, hallmarks), detailed descriptions of materials and condition, and a stated return or authenticity policy. Reviews and reputation matter—check for consistency and responsiveness." }, { type: "p", text: "Avoid deals that seem too good to be true. Vintage gold and genuine stones have a market value; prices that are far below that often indicate plated, filled, or misrepresented pieces. When in doubt, ask questions and request additional photos or documentation." }, { type: "h2", text: "Protecting Your Purchase" }, { type: "p", text: "Use secure payment methods. Keep records of your order, photos, and any correspondence. If a piece arrives and does not match the description, contact the seller immediately. Reputable dealers like SÁV+ stand behind their descriptions and will work with you to resolve issues." }, { type: "h3", text: "Shopping SÁV+ Online" }, { type: "p", text: "At SÁV+ we curate every piece for quality and authenticity. Descriptions are clear, photos are accurate, and we are committed to your satisfaction. Explore our vintage and estate collection online and buy with confidence." }], [1, 3], [{ question: "Is it safe to buy vintage jewelry online?", answer: "Yes, when you buy from established, specialized dealers with clear descriptions, photos, and policies. Avoid unknown sellers and too-good-to-be-true prices." }, { question: "What should I look for in an online vintage jewelry listing?", answer: "Multiple photos (including hallmarks), material and condition description, return policy, and seller reputation. Ask questions if anything is unclear." }, { question: "What if the piece doesn’t match the description?", answer: "Contact the seller immediately. Reputable dealers will work to resolve the issue, including returns or adjustments. Keep records of your order and communication." }]);
const buyingOnlineEs = p("buying-vintage-online", "es", "comprar-joyas-vintage-online-forma-segura", "Comprar Joyas Vintage Online de Forma Segura: Guía de Confianza y Autenticidad", "Cómo comprar joyería vintage y de herencia online con confianza. Señales de alerta, señales de confianza y proteger tu compra.", [{ type: "h2", text: "Elegir vendedores de confianza" }, { type: "p", text: "Compra a comerciantes establecidos o plataformas curadas especializadas en joyería vintage y de herencia. Busca fotos claras, descripciones detalladas de materiales y estado, y una política de devolución o autenticidad. Las reseñas y la reputación importan." }, { type: "p", text: "Evita ofertas que parezcan demasiado buenas para ser verdad. El oro vintage y las piedras genuinas tienen un valor de mercado; precios muy por debajo suelen indicar piezas bañadas, laminadas o mal representadas." }, { type: "h2", text: "Proteger tu compra" }, { type: "p", text: "Usa métodos de pago seguros. Guarda registros de tu pedido, fotos y correspondencia. Si una pieza llega y no coincide con la descripción, contacta al vendedor de inmediato. Comerciantes serios como SÁV+ respaldan sus descripciones." }, { type: "h3", text: "Comprar en SÁV+ online" }, { type: "p", text: "En SÁV+ seleccionamos cada pieza por calidad y autenticidad. Las descripciones son claras y las fotos precisas. Explora nuestra colección vintage y de herencia online." }], [1, 3], [{ question: "¿Es seguro comprar joyería vintage online?", answer: "Sí, cuando compras a comerciantes establecidos y especializados con descripciones claras, fotos y políticas. Evita vendedores desconocidos y precios demasiado buenos." }, { question: "¿Qué debo buscar en un anuncio de joyería vintage online?", answer: "Fotos múltiples (incluyendo contrastes), descripción de materiales y estado, política de devolución y reputación del vendedor." }, { question: "¿Y si la pieza no coincide con la descripción?", answer: "Contacta al vendedor de inmediato. Los comerciantes serios trabajarán para resolver el problema, incluyendo devoluciones. Guarda registros." }]);

// —— 27. The SÁV+ Curation Process ——
const savCurationEn = p("sav-curation-process", "en", "the-sav-curation-process", "The SÁV+ Curation Process: How We Select Your Jewelry", "How SÁV+ chooses vintage and estate pieces. Quality, authenticity, and the standards behind every piece we offer.", [{ type: "h2", text: "What We Look For" }, { type: "p", text: "Every piece at SÁV+ is selected for quality of materials, authenticity, and design. We focus on fine metals—gold, platinum, and sterling silver—and genuine stones. We avoid plated or filled pieces unless clearly described as such, and we do not offer costume or fake jewelry. Condition matters: we prefer pieces that are intact, wearable, and repairable when needed." }, { type: "p", text: "We look for design that stands the test of time: Art Deco geometry, Victorian sentiment, mid-century simplicity, and one-of-a-kind estate finds. Our goal is to offer jewelry you can wear with confidence and pass down with pride." }, { type: "h2", text: "From Source to You" }, { type: "p", text: "We source from trusted channels and evaluate each piece for hallmarks, construction, and wear. We describe materials and condition clearly and provide photos that show the piece accurately. When you buy from SÁV+, you buy from a team that stands behind what we sell and is committed to your satisfaction." }, { type: "h3", text: "Explore the Collection" }, { type: "p", text: "Our curated collection reflects our standards: vintage and estate jewelry for discerning collectors in Florida and beyond. Shop with confidence and discover pieces that combine beauty, quality, and authenticity." }], [1, 2], [{ question: "How does SÁV+ verify authenticity?", answer: "We evaluate hallmarks, construction, materials, and condition. We source from trusted channels and describe each piece accurately. We stand behind our descriptions." }, { question: "Does SÁV+ sell plated or costume jewelry?", answer: "We focus on fine metals and genuine stones. We do not sell costume or misrepresented jewelry. Any non-solid pieces would be clearly described." }, { question: "Where does SÁV+ source its jewelry?", answer: "We source through trusted estate and vintage channels. Every piece is selected and described to meet our quality and authenticity standards." }]);
const savCurationEs = p("sav-curation-process", "es", "el-proceso-de-curaduria-sav", "El Proceso de Curaduría de SÁV+: Cómo Seleccionamos Tu Joyería", "Cómo SÁV+ elige las piezas vintage y de herencia. Calidad, autenticidad y los estándares detrás de cada pieza que ofrecemos.", [{ type: "h2", text: "Qué buscamos" }, { type: "p", text: "Cada pieza en SÁV+ se selecciona por calidad de materiales, autenticidad y diseño. Nos enfocamos en metales finos y piedras genuinas. Evitamos piezas chapadas o laminadas salvo que se describan claramente. La condición importa: preferimos piezas intactas, llevables y reparables." }, { type: "p", text: "Buscamos diseño que resiste el paso del tiempo: geometría Art Decó, sentimiento victoriano, simplicidad mid-century y hallazgos de herencia únicos." }, { type: "h2", text: "De la fuente a ti" }, { type: "p", text: "Nos abastecemos por canales de confianza y evaluamos cada pieza por contrastes, construcción y desgaste. Describimos materiales y estado con claridad. Cuando compras en SÁV+, compras a un equipo que respalda lo que vende." }, { type: "h3", text: "Explora la colección" }, { type: "p", text: "Nuestra colección curada refleja nuestros estándares. Compra con confianza y descubre piezas que combinan belleza, calidad y autenticidad." }], [1, 2], [{ question: "¿Cómo verifica SÁV+ la autenticidad?", answer: "Evaluamos contrastes, construcción, materiales y estado. Nos abastecemos por canales de confianza y describimos cada pieza con precisión." }, { question: "¿SÁV+ vende joyería chapada o de bisutería?", answer: "Nos enfocamos en metales finos y piedras genuinas. No vendemos bisutería ni joyería mal representada." }, { question: "¿De dónde se abastece SÁV+?", answer: "Nos abastecemos por canales de herencia y vintage de confianza. Cada pieza se selecciona y describe según nuestros estándares de calidad y autenticidad." }]);

// —— 28. Choosing Jewelry for Anniversaries ——
const anniversariesEn = p("jewelry-for-anniversaries", "en", "choosing-jewelry-for-anniversaries", "Choosing Jewelry for Anniversaries: Traditions and Ideas", "Traditional anniversary metals and gems, plus why vintage and estate pieces make meaningful gifts.", [{ type: "h2", text: "Traditional Anniversary Gifts" }, { type: "p", text: "Anniversary traditions often assign materials by year: paper (1), cotton (2), leather (3), and eventually gold (50) and diamond (60). In between, modern lists include gemstones like ruby (40), sapphire (45), and emerald (55). Jewelry can incorporate these materials—a gold necklace for a 50th, a ruby ring for a 40th—making it a lasting and personal gift." }, { type: "p", text: "Vintage and estate jewelry fits anniversary giving especially well. A period piece—Art Deco for a 1920s-themed anniversary, or a Victorian locket for a romantic milestone—adds narrative and uniqueness. You can often find better quality and more distinctive design in vintage than in many new pieces." }, { type: "h2", text: "Making It Personal" }, { type: "p", text: "Consider your partner’s style, the milestone year, and whether you want something they can wear daily or for special occasions. Vintage rings, necklaces, bracelets, and brooches offer a range of options. Have pieces resized or repaired as needed so they are ready to wear." }, { type: "h3", text: "Find Anniversary Jewelry at SÁV+" }, { type: "p", text: "At SÁV+ we curate vintage and estate jewelry for every occasion. Whether you are celebrating one year or fifty, explore our collection for pieces that honor the milestone and the person you love." }], [1, 3], [{ question: "What is the traditional 25th anniversary gift?", answer: "Silver is traditional for the 25th. A silver necklace, bracelet, or pair of earrings from our vintage collection could be a meaningful gift." }, { question: "Why give vintage jewelry for an anniversary?", answer: "Vintage pieces are unique, often have better quality and design for the price, and carry history that can symbolize a lasting relationship." }, { question: "Can vintage anniversary jewelry be resized?", answer: "Many vintage rings and bracelets can be resized by a skilled jeweler. Check with the seller; we can advise on sizing options for our pieces." }]);
const anniversariesEs = p("jewelry-for-anniversaries", "es", "elegir-joyas-para-aniversarios", "Elegir Joyas para Aniversarios: Tradiciones e Ideas", "Metales y gemas tradicionales por aniversario, y por qué las piezas vintage y de herencia son regalos con significado.", [{ type: "h2", text: "Regalos tradicionales de aniversario" }, { type: "p", text: "Las tradiciones de aniversario asignan materiales por año: oro (50), diamante (60). Las listas modernas incluyen rubí (40), zafiro (45), esmeralda (55). La joyería puede incorporar estos materiales. La joyería vintage y de herencia encaja muy bien con los regalos de aniversario." }, { type: "p", text: "Una pieza de época añade narrativa y singularidad. Puedes encontrar mejor calidad y diseño más distintivo en vintage que en muchas piezas nuevas." }, { type: "h2", text: "Hacerlo personal" }, { type: "p", text: "Considera el estilo de tu pareja, el año del hito y si quieres algo para llevar a diario o para ocasiones especiales. Los anillos, collares, pulseras y broches vintage ofrecen opciones. Haz cambiar de talla o reparar cuando haga falta." }, { type: "h3", text: "Encuentra joyas de aniversario en SÁV+" }, { type: "p", text: "En SÁV+ seleccionamos joyería vintage y de herencia para cada ocasión. Ya celebres un año o cincuenta, explora nuestra colección." }], [1, 3], [{ question: "¿Cuál es el regalo tradicional del 25º aniversario?", answer: "La plata es tradicional para el 25º. Un collar, pulsera o pendientes de plata vintage pueden ser un regalo con significado." }, { question: "¿Por qué regalar joyería vintage en un aniversario?", answer: "Las piezas vintage son únicas, a menudo tienen mejor calidad y diseño por el precio, y llevan historia que puede simbolizar una relación duradera." }, { question: "¿Se puede cambiar la talla de joyería vintage de aniversario?", answer: "Muchos anillos y pulseras vintage pueden cambiarse de talla por un joyero hábil. Consulta con el vendedor." }]);

// —— 29. Modern Vintage in Miami Scene ——
const miamiEn = p("modern-vintage-miami", "en", "modern-vintage-in-miami-scene", "Modern Vintage in the Miami Scene: Where Old Meets New", "Miami’s fashion and jewelry culture embraces vintage alongside new design. How the city wears and shops estate jewelry.", [{ type: "h2", text: "Miami’s Jewelry Culture" }, { type: "p", text: "Miami is a city of contrast: bold new architecture and design alongside a deep appreciation for vintage and collectible pieces. The fashion scene mixes high-end new with one-of-a-kind vintage; jewelry is no exception. Art Deco and mid-century pieces fit the city’s glamorous, tropical aesthetic, while estate jewelry from Europe and the Americas finds a ready audience." }, { type: "p", text: "From Wynwood to the Design District, Miami residents and visitors shop for statement pieces that stand out. Vintage and estate jewelry offers uniqueness that mass-produced new pieces cannot match." }, { type: "h2", text: "Wearing Vintage in Miami" }, { type: "p", text: "Vintage gold, colored stones, and bold designs pair well with Miami’s casual-luxury style. Layered necklaces, chunky bracelets, and standout rings are common. Estate pieces from the 1920s–1970s especially resonate—they have the glamour and character that fit the city’s vibe." }, { type: "h3", text: "Finding Vintage in Miami and Online" }, { type: "p", text: "Miami has local dealers and boutiques; online curated collections like SÁV+ also serve the city and the rest of Florida. Whether you are in Miami or shopping from elsewhere, explore our vintage and estate collection for pieces that capture the modern-vintage spirit." }], [1, 3], [{ question: "Is Miami good for vintage jewelry?", answer: "Yes. Miami has a strong fashion and jewelry culture that embraces vintage and estate pieces alongside new design. Dealers and buyers are active in the area." }, { question: "What style of vintage jewelry is popular in Miami?", answer: "Art Deco, mid-century, and bold statement pieces fit Miami’s glamorous, tropical aesthetic. Gold and colored stones are especially popular." }, { question: "Can I buy Miami-style vintage jewelry online?", answer: "Yes. Curated platforms like SÁV+ offer vintage and estate jewelry to Miami and beyond. You can shop the same quality and style from anywhere." }]);
const miamiEs = p("modern-vintage-miami", "es", "vintage-moderno-escena-miami", "El Vintage Moderno en la Escena de Miami: Donde lo Viejo Encuentra lo Nuevo", "La cultura de moda y joyería de Miami abraza el vintage junto al diseño nuevo. Cómo la ciudad lleva y compra joyería de herencia.", [{ type: "h2", text: "La cultura de joyería de Miami" }, { type: "p", text: "Miami es una ciudad de contraste: arquitectura y diseño nuevos y atrevidos junto a una gran apreciación por las piezas vintage y coleccionables. La escena de moda mezcla lo nuevo de alta gama con vintage único; la joyería no es excepción. Las piezas Art Decó y mid-century encajan con la estética glamorosa y tropical de la ciudad." }, { type: "p", text: "Desde Wynwood al Design District, residentes y visitantes compran piezas de impacto. La joyería vintage y de herencia ofrece singularidad que las piezas nuevas de producción masiva no pueden igualar." }, { type: "h2", text: "Llevar vintage en Miami" }, { type: "p", text: "El oro vintage, las piedras de color y los diseños atrevidos combinan bien con el estilo casual-lujo de Miami. Collares en capas, pulseras gruesas y anillos destacados son comunes. Las piezas de herencia de los años 20–70 resuenan especialmente." }, { type: "h3", text: "Encontrar vintage en Miami y online" }, { type: "p", text: "Miami tiene comerciantes y boutiques locales; las colecciones online curadas como SÁV+ también sirven a la ciudad y al resto de Florida. Explora nuestra colección vintage y de herencia." }], [1, 3], [{ question: "¿Miami es buena para joyería vintage?", answer: "Sí. Miami tiene una cultura de moda y joyería fuerte que abraza piezas vintage y de herencia junto al diseño nuevo." }, { question: "¿Qué estilo de joyería vintage es popular en Miami?", answer: "Art Decó, mid-century y piezas de impacto atrevidas encajan con la estética glamorosa y tropical de Miami." }, { question: "¿Puedo comprar joyería vintage estilo Miami online?", answer: "Sí. Plataformas curadas como SÁV+ ofrecen joyería vintage y de herencia a Miami y más allá." }]);

// —— 30. Why Your Engagement Ring Should Be Vintage ——
const engagementEn = p("engagement-ring-vintage", "en", "why-your-engagement-ring-should-be-vintage", "Why Your Engagement Ring Should Be Vintage", "Unique design, better value, and a story. Why more couples are choosing vintage and estate engagement rings.", [{ type: "h2", text: "Uniqueness and Character" }, { type: "p", text: "A vintage engagement ring is unlike any other. Old European and old mine cut diamonds have a distinct sparkle; Art Deco and Edwardian settings offer design that is no longer made. You avoid the look of mass-produced mall jewelry and get a ring that reflects your personal style and story." }, { type: "p", text: "Many couples also appreciate the sustainability of choosing a ring that already exists. No new mining or manufacturing is required—you give a piece of the past a new chapter." }, { type: "h2", text: "Value and Quality" }, { type: "p", text: "Vintage engagement rings often offer better value than comparable new rings. You can get higher quality metal and stones, or more distinctive design, for the same budget. Estate rings have already stood the test of time; with care, they will last for generations." }, { type: "h3", text: "Finding Your Vintage Engagement Ring" }, { type: "p", text: "Look for rings that suit your partner’s style and hand. Consider resizing options and have the ring checked by a jeweler before proposing. At SÁV+ we curate vintage and estate rings that are ready to become the symbol of your commitment. Explore our collection and find a ring that is as unique as your love story." }], [1, 3], [{ question: "Are vintage engagement rings durable?", answer: "Yes. Quality vintage rings in gold or platinum with secure settings are made to last. Have prongs and shanks checked by a jeweler and resize if needed." }, { question: "Can I resize a vintage engagement ring?", answer: "Many vintage rings can be resized one or two sizes. Plain bands and simple shanks are easiest; eternity bands and some designs cannot be resized. A jeweler can advise." }, { question: "Where can I find vintage engagement rings?", answer: "Estate jewelry dealers and curated collections like SÁV+ offer vintage engagement rings. Look for clear descriptions, photos, and sizing information." }]);
const engagementEs = p("engagement-ring-vintage", "es", "por-que-tu-anillo-compromiso-debe-ser-vintage", "Por qué tu Anillo de Compromiso debe ser Vintage", "Diseño único, mejor valor y una historia. Por qué más parejas eligen anillos de compromiso vintage y de herencia.", [{ type: "h2", text: "Singularidad y carácter" }, { type: "p", text: "Un anillo de compromiso vintage no se parece a ningún otro. Los diamantes old European y old mine tienen un brillo distinto; los engastes Art Decó y eduardianos ofrecen diseño que ya no se hace. Evitas el aspecto de la joyería de centro comercial y obtienes un anillo que refleja tu estilo e historia." }, { type: "p", text: "Muchas parejas también valoran la sostenibilidad de elegir un anillo que ya existe. No se requiere nueva minería ni fabricación." }, { type: "h2", text: "Valor y calidad" }, { type: "p", text: "Los anillos de compromiso vintage suelen ofrecer mejor valor que anillos nuevos comparables. Puedes obtener metal y piedras de mayor calidad, o diseño más distintivo, por el mismo presupuesto." }, { type: "h3", text: "Encontrar tu anillo de compromiso vintage" }, { type: "p", text: "Busca anillos que encajen con el estilo y la mano de tu pareja. Considera opciones de talla y haz que un joyero revise el anillo antes de proponer. En SÁV+ seleccionamos anillos vintage y de herencia listos para ser el símbolo de tu compromiso. Explora nuestra colección." }], [1, 3], [{ question: "¿Los anillos de compromiso vintage son resistentes?", answer: "Sí. Los anillos vintage de calidad en oro o platino con engastes seguros están hechos para durar. Haz revisar garras y uña por un joyero." }, { question: "¿Puedo cambiar la talla de un anillo de compromiso vintage?", answer: "Muchos anillos vintage pueden cambiarse uno o dos números. Las alianzas lisas y uñas simples son más fáciles; las bandas eternity y algunos diseños no pueden. Un joyero puede asesorar." }, { question: "¿Dónde encontrar anillos de compromiso vintage?", answer: "Comerciantes de joyería de herencia y colecciones curadas como SÁV+ ofrecen anillos de compromiso vintage. Busca descripciones claras, fotos e información de talla." }]);

